flag small_base
  description: Choose the new smaller, split-up base package.
 
Executable mkcabal
    main-is:             mkcabal.hs
    build-depends:       mtl, pcre-light>=0.3, readline
    if flag(small_base)
        build-depends: base >= 3,
                       pretty, old-locale, old-time, directory
    else
        build-depends: base < 3


